title: Sur Sports Complex
text: The Sur Sports Complex is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Sur%2C%20Oman">Sur</a>, <a href="Oman">Oman</a>. It is used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Oman%20Professional%20League">Oman Professional League</a> side <a href="Sur%20%28football%20club%29">Sur FC</a>. The stadium has a capacity of 8,000 people and was opened in 1996.
